WorkItem.ClosedComment:
Fixed in SVN for BIFF8 (Excel 97 - Excel 2003)

Support is now similar to that of PHPExcel_Reader_Excel2007, meaning:

Named cell: ok
Named range: ok
Named formula: can not be read
WorkItem.Description: Currently Excel5 reader is not reading named ranges (defined names). This gives problems when formulas in the spreadsheet contain names.
WorkItem.Summary: Support for named ranges (defined names) in PHPExcel_Reader_Excel5
